# Testing Rules

## Requirements
```rules
testing:
  coverage:
    minimum: 80%
    report: true
    exclude: ["__init__.py", "setup.py"]
  
  types:
    unit: required
    integration: required
    e2e: recommended
    
  frameworks:
    main: pytest
    async: pytest-asyncio
    coverage: pytest-cov
```

## Test Structure
```rules
test_organization:
  files:
    pattern: "test_*.py"
    location: "tests/{module}"
    
  functions:
    pattern: "test_*"
    async_pattern: "test_async_*"
    
  fixtures:
    scope: [function, class, module, session]
    naming: "fixture_*"
``` 